{
  "stem": "18102.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS] The way it went-- the way it went is that my, my mother woke me in the middle of that night to tell me and dress me-- it was like 2:00 AM-- that we were going to say goodbye to my father.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until then I didn't know he was leaving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they kept that from me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I dressed in the middle of the night, and it was that night that stands out most in my mind because as we walked through the deserted Bialystok streets, I could hear the machine gun fire and the airplanes above.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a war scene, and it stands out in my memory because the gunfire echoed through the buildings as we walked.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you couldn't tell where it was coming from because there was a constant echoing going on as if it was coming from every direction.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was a most frightening, probably the most frightening, night of my life 'til then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a little over--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--seven.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we arrived at a, at a designated place where there was this big truck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I could only see the outlines of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is pitch black, and it's in the middle of the night and a lot of people milling around and everybody hugging and saying goodbye.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was then that my father said goodbye.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My, my mother had advised me and told me that my father was leaving and the reason for that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said goodbye to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a very quick-- in my memory-- a very quick goodbye that didn't last very long.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father wasn't a hugger anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was not the kind that would spend a lot of time at hugging someone.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
